text.value: This was a great experience, such an amazing atmosphere. Greeted with smiles all around, the waitress was great, the owner stopped by and told me the special, but I was only in the mood for salad and pizza. This pizza was great, crispy, the right amount of sauce and cheese. I am looking forward to coming back and trying other dishes that they have, I will also try a drink next time. They truly go out of their way to make you feel like family. Such a great place!

text.value: First time there tonight and will definitely be back! The pizza was great- think crust and fresh. Customer service was pleasant and warm- the owner and staff made it a point to check in frequently. My daughter keeps asking when we could go back because the staff gave her an opportunity to help out and observe what the waitress does! She felt included and of course, thrived on the attention. Love the touch of the garage door that opens to let fresh air in!
